Seq1.CallerContent: Hi, Dominique. My name is Ms. Watson. I'm calling in regard to an outstanding invoice. I keep getting this invoice, and the office says that they're corrected, and they haven't.
Seq1.ReceiverContent: Okay, I got you, ma'am. Come on, give me a minute. Let me transfer the call to a concerned person who can help you out with this. Thanks. I'll miss you online. I'm transferring the call, and you have a great day.
